Bright Mountain Media, Inc. Key Developments

Bright Mountain Media, Inc. Announces Resignation of Randolph A. Pohlman from the Board of Directors
Jun 5 17
On June 2, 2017, Dr. Randolph A. Pohlman resigned from the Board of Directors of Bright Mountain Media, Inc. for personal reasons. Dr. Pohlman had been a member of the Board of Directors since March 2015 and served as the Chairman of the Audit Committee of the Board.


Bright Mountain Media, Inc. announced delayed 10-Q filing
May 16 17
On 05/16/2017, Bright Mountain Media, Inc. announced that they will be unable to file their next 10-Q by the deadline required by the SEC.


Bright Mountain Media, Inc. announced delayed 10-Q filing
Nov 15 16
On 11/15/2016, Bright Mountain Media, Inc. announced that they will be unable to file their next 10-Q by the deadline required by the SEC.


